{"tid":957931,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱係西鐵見到兩個好有禮貌嘅年輕人","createTime":"2018-12-27T11:41:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T14:03:08.000Z","uid":160760,"like":175,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"42dd6976bb35112cece0e02f19b7d7d99c4b3745","tid":957931,"uid":160760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"事源係咁嘅，有個阿姨係西鐵走嗰陣漏咗個袋係張櫈到，然後嗰兩個年輕人即刻大嗌嗰個阿姨叫佢拎返個袋，全程都勁有禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n但係個阿姨走咗之後，佢哋就即刻好大聲咁笑個阿姨on9，話佢連個袋都漏得。<br />\n<br />\n然後我睇到呢個情形，一方面又好欣賞佢哋咁有禮貌提個阿姨，但一方面又覺得咁大聲咁笑人好仆街，因為係笑到成個車箱都聽到，搞到我好矛盾，唔知點看待佢哋好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嗰兩個年輕人值得欣賞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：背後笑返人，正仆街<br />\n<br />\n利伸：玩緊手機先冇留意到個阿姨漏咗個袋，如果唔係都會提佢。"},{"pid":"d3708e7517441ab349a989c9c823d375c206810e","tid":957931,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bf7f470d893e43dc47d0aeb702ddadb51081382","tid":957931,"uid":16061,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:43:31.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔提佢 等佢唔見袋加埋比人笑囉<br />\n你老母你有無腦嫁 拎返個袋比人笑下有咩所謂 何況個阿嬸又唔撚知"},{"pid":"7ce7ca89d33d5147e728f3e6221f061e4cc640cc","tid":957931,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"咁你想點呀？"},{"pid":"9e55f4ec143a5dd97207f4d038f74ba47f337edc","tid":957931,"uid":132587,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:57:38.000Z","msg":"無傷大雅 大家都開心 我覺得無乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ab57aa8b337bcc31a7a0be984497a4b6ff1538","tid":957931,"uid":208722,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"笑下又唔撚畀，對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次唔撚提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj